{"tid":2501340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"清算港台︱李百全料最快下月「重整」電視部 《視點31》或停播","createTime":"2021-04-23T09:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:49:12.000Z","uid":67963,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c6fbd03f2ecdcde343527f08653b6e5a06d988","tid":2501340,"uid":67963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/CDQIJNUFNZEF5OQAFXHJ2LNPUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FCDQIJNUFNZEF5OQAFXHJ2LNPUA%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=2c3eb10a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FCDQIJNUFNZEF5OQAFXHJ2LNPUA%2F&h=4fa90144\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/CDQIJNUFNZEF5OQAFXHJ2LNPUA/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣播處長李百全擬再大舉整頓港台電視部。《蘋果》獲悉，李百全擬「開大技」，最快下月將「重整」電視部，主力負責時事節目的公共事務組成為重災區，《視點31》及《早辰。早晨》或將會停播......<br />\n<br />\n多個港台消息向《蘋果》透露，李百全即將重整電視部的消息在內部已沸沸揚揚，但管理層暫時未有明確交代。有知情人士指，自李百全上任後，公共事務組不少高層管理層遞交辭職信，包括公共事務組總監王祿霞、《頭條新聞》資深監製廖慧玲、《香港故事》監製方曉山等，將於下月先後離職。管理層遂以公共事務組人手不足為由，打算減少公共事務組的節目，包括取消《視點31》及《早辰。早晨》。王牌節目《鏗鏘集》及《議事論事》料獲保留......<br />\n<br />\n另一港台中人表示，<span class=\"red\">整頓後的公共事務組，預料只餘三個節目，除《鏗鏘集》和《議事論事》外，《城市論壇》料「有得留低」。至於傳出會被停播的《視點31》和《早辰。早晨》，則未清楚「大限」，但估計大整頓會是下月中開展，因屆時已遞信的公共事務組高層陸續離職</span>......"},{"pid":"5b71dd2dc22270884943f0ecf50f327bb909a6c1","tid":2501340,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"直接轉播CCAV咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44079fbc37b762b7f4f97975a0f4d5907bc87d5","tid":2501340,"uid":161726,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"停左個港台佢啦<br />\n都冇人睇"},{"pid":"f1bb29d0eb17aec22578a97ef83e9c922b3d3b99","tid":2501340,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f98fd168c564f6419942e6ff499bd42cf80017","tid":2501340,"uid":67963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"根本就係滅咗公共事務組<br />\n<br />\n另一個想踩住同事條屍想上位嘅<br />\n睇黎見勢色唔對, 唔想做 Condom<br />\n<br />\n區麗雅傳長請病假至8月<br />\n<br />\n另外，港台今再向員工發通告，掌管電視部的助理廣播處長區麗雅放假，由總監（電視）陳俊樂署理其職位。據了解，區是請病假。另港台消息人士指，區上周曾請了一星期病假，之後請假至8月，未知是請病假還是放大假，又說通告上未有如往常般，寫明陳署理職位的限期，做法不尋常，質疑區自李百全上任後同樣備受批評，有傳區想調回電台部，今次請長假未知是否想避過電視部被整頓。"},{"pid":"e398a6fe5130c962a44de7c9a42100780ec8f441","tid":2501340,"uid":67963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"31 台走個風格係 BBC 2<br />\n你睇佢播啲節目<br />\n有深度, 講知識, 講內容<br />\n<br />\n即係現政權最憎嘅野<br />\n<br />\n參考: <br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BBC_Two#Programming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBBC_Two%23Programming&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ee98706d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BBC_Two#Programming</a><br />\n<br />\nBBC Two's remit is to be a mixed-genre channel appealing to a broad adult audience with programmes of depth and substance. It should carry the greatest amount and range of knowledge building programming of any BBC television channel, complemented by distinctive comedy, drama and arts programming.<br />\n&mdash; BBC Two remit"},{"pid":"3f4bbcb4e6aebe0ef7edac5bb29f53c729824bb8","tid":2501340,"uid":67963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b44079fbc37b762b7f4f97975a0f4d5907bc87d5","tid":2501340,"uid":161726,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"停左個港台佢啦<br />\n都冇人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n政府會霸住晒黎做佢啲宣傳廣播<br />\n無人睇就遲啲迫人睇"},{"pid":"640e0be4b7387eabf6f4c8734002b35c22186c23","tid":2501340,"uid":67963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b71dd2dc22270884943f0ecf50f327bb909a6c1","tid":2501340